snippet: Sarah Palin and the Tea Party movement have so far shown little impact on the 2012 Republican presidential campaign.
abstract: Sarah Palin and the Tea Party movement have so far shown little impact on the 2012 Republican presidential campaign.
lead_paragraph: In October, Sarah Palin announced that she would not run for president in 2012, ending the media frenzy around her potential candidacy even as she vowed to remain politically active and influential.

headline.main: Influence of Palin and Tea Party Wanes in Early Contests
